    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "これもいい感じだし……あ、こっちも可愛い！\nう～ん、迷っちゃうな～",
      "startTime": 7.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "デザイナーさんって凄いね",
      "startTime": 12.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなのイメージを伝えただけで\nこんなにいっぱいアイデアを出せるなんて！",
      "startTime": 17.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（月ストとサニピに）\n（夏フェスのオファーがかかった）",
      "startTime": 22.0334333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ビーチでのイベントのため、新しい夏用衣装の意見を）\n（みんなに聞いているんだが……）",
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あ\nこの衣装可愛いけど、この部分はいらないかも",
      "startTime": 33.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは踊るのに邪魔になっちゃうかな～\nここを取って～、こっちももっとスッキリさせて～",
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "動きやすさも考えないとだし……そうだ！\nここからここまですっぱりカットしちゃうとか！",
      "startTime": 53.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら、さすがに露出が多過ぎるぞ",
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　でもさー\n{user}さんは見たくないの？",
      "startTime": 64.1,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}